import Container from 'react-bootstrap/Container';
import Row from 'react-bootstrap/Row';
import Col from 'react-bootstrap/Col';

const Home = () => (

    <Row>
      <Col>1 of 2</Col>
      <Col>2 of 2</Col>
    </Row>
    <Row>
      <Col>1 of 3</Col>
      <Col>2 of 3</Col>
      <Col>3 of 3</Col>
    </Row>
  </Container>
)

export default Home
